&lt;p&gt;Now we’re entering the next phase.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a Head of Talent Acquisition to help transform recruiting into a true hiring engine — one that can support rapid global scaling while continuously improving quality, speed, efficiency, and candidate experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Headcount growth continues at roughly 30% year-over-year, with a significant focus on AI talent globally. This role is critical in helping the company scale intelligently and competitively in one of the fastest-moving talent markets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is not a traditional recruiting management role focused only on delivery. We are looking for someone who can think strategically, operate hands-on, and leverage AI and automation to modernize how recruiting works. You will lead and develop a growing global TA team, partner closely with leadership across the company, and help redefine how we attract and hire top talent at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
