&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Data Management and Integration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with cloud backend engineering teams to design ETL pipelines that move and transform data efficiently across different storage systems.&lt;/li&gt;
